title: Vegas Future Bets, HOF recap, Coleman traded, Benjamin blunder (Football 08/06)
description:
A very raspy Will Brinson breaks down the future bets he made in Las Vegas over the weekend, and also gives a recap of the Hall of Fame induction ceremony as well as a breakdown of the Corey Coleman trade, Kelvin Benjamin's blunder and much more.
